    print(f"Success! Website generated at: {OUTPUT_FILE}")

if __name__ == "__main__":
    generate_mohangraphy()
Final Checklist
Wait for DNS Propagation: It can take anywhere from 1 to 24 hours for the new domain to start working globally.

Enforce HTTPS: Once the domain is linked, go back to GitHub Settings > Pages and check the box for Enforce HTTPS. This gives your site the "Lock" icon in the browser, making it secure for visitors.

